#, no-c-format
msgid "Create preliminary .cvsignore in the current directory"
msgstr "Crea un .cvsignore preliminar no cartafol actual."

#. Tag: title
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Descrición"

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:34
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> is used to create a preliminary "
"<filename>.cvsignore</filename> in the current directory. It does this based "
"on certain contents it finds in <filename>Makefile.am</filename>"
msgstr ""
"<command>create_cvsignore</command> úsase para crear un <filename>."
"cvsignore</filename> no cartafol actual. Faino con base en certos contidos "
"que atopa no <filename>Makefile.am</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"No lines will be removed from any existing <filename>.cvsignore</filename>. "
"If there is not already a <filename>.cvsignore</filename> file, it will be "
"added to the cvs repository."
msgstr ""
"Non se retirará ningunha liña de ningún <filename>.cvsignore</filename> xa "
"existente. Se aínda non hai un ficheiro <filename>.cvsignore</filename>, "
"engadirase ao repositorio cvs."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that you must have a <filename>Makefile.am</filename> in the current "
"directory for this tool to work."
msgstr ""
"Lembre que debe ter un <filename>Makefile.am</filename> no cartafol actual "
"para que esta ferramenta funcione."

#. Tag: para
#: man-create_cvsignore.1.docbook:46
#, no-c-format
msgid "This utility is part of the &kde; Software Development Kit."
msgstr ""
"Esta utilidade forma parte do equipamento de desenvolvemento de programas de "
"&kde;."

